data.description: Looking for a move-in ready home??? This remodeled home is a short drive to Target and the $20 Billion Intel Project.  It's PACKED with character and has high ceilings, original hardwood floors, crown molding, thick trim/baseboard, tall windows, gas fireplace, and an open floor plan. It offers 4 beds, 1.5 baths, 1600 living sqft, partially finished basement, fenced yard, and a large wraparound front porch. The massive kitchen has been renovated and offers new cabinets, granite cabinets, SS appliances, new light fixtures, sleek backsplash, new sink, new fixtures, and plenty of storage. The luxurious bathroom offers a large shower & full body shower system, floor-to-ceiling tile, new vanity, bluetooth exhaust fan, and new toilet. Other updates: newer roof, newer HVAC, vinyl windows, & more!
